All Classes

Class Summary
Class Description
Auth
Helps with setting up the JSON config file with API key(s) for the services required by BTTN.
BTTN
The main class of the program which runs the program, helps with setting up the JSON config file, and reading the JSON file to get user specific data.
Bundle
Helper class used to help when using the resource bundle to help support multiple languages
Channel
Helps with modifying channels to be checked for changed live status
Helper
Helper class, which focuses on retrieving data required throughout the program
HTTP
Helper class to help with making HTTP get and post requests
Logger
Logs info, warnings and error messages to a log file.
Notifications
Handles sending notifications for new live channels, BTTN update, or errors checking for live status changes
Updater
Helps with checking for updates and letting the user know that an update is available
